command: CREATE DATABASE IF NOT EXISTS temp_db

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS temp_table (
            id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
            data VARCHAR(100)
        )

CREATE VIEW view_data AS
        SELECT data FROM temp_table

CREATE PROCEDURE SelectAll()
        BEGIN
            SELECT * FROM temp_table;
        END

CREATE TRIGGER BeforeInsert
        BEFORE INSERT ON temp_table FOR EACH ROW
        SET NEW.data = CONCAT('Prefix_', NEW.data)
ALTER TABLE temp_table ADD COLUMN new_column VARCHAR(100)
ALTER TABLE temp_table DROP COLUMN new_column
UPDATE countries SET population = 654321 WHERE name = 'Testland'

INSERT INTO countries (name, population) VALUES ('Testland', 123456)
            ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE population = VALUES(population)
UPDATE countries SET population = 200 WHERE name = 'TempCountry'
